content: I'm on discord. No sign of scale to win. How do I start textiong. Discord keeps askimg me to verify my account.  I texted for Biden 4 years go - it was not nearly this confusing.

HI <@1281369272999870464> I appreciate your confusion with Discord, there is a lot going on here. it takes a little time to onboard everyone after training, and you should see a direct message (DM) from the team when they are ready for you.
